The National State of Disaster regulations to address the country's energy crisis have finally been released. There's some relief though for public health facilities, as over two hundred of them will be exempted from power cuts. Manqoba Mchunu reports. #eNCA Courtesy #DStv403  JOHANNESBURG - The National State of Disaster regulations to address the country's energy crisis has finally been released. There's some relief though for public health facilities, as over 200 of them will be exempt from power cuts. Watch the video above for more details.